{
  "text": "The exploration of constraints on the higher-derivative corrections to simple models such as Einstein-Maxwell or Einstein-Maxwell-dilaton (EMD) 14 theories inspired by 13 The positivity of this variable is to be expected when the perturbation is due to the inclusion of higher-derivative operators motivated by the UV-completion of the effective theory -see [CITATION_1] .",
